description: Try our easy to follow Smoked Salmon & Quke Canapes recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Smoked Salmon & Quke Canapes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: In a small bowl, mix crème fraîche with wasabi. Slice salmon into 1cm strips, then twist strips and place on top of Quke halves. Dollop with crème fraîche mixture and scatter over chives.
